Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.04,0:00:18.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.92,0:00:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You called me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.59,0:00:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.26,0:00:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You broke the seal!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.59,0:00:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.26,0:00:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pledge yourself to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.89,0:00:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... No! NO!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.27,0:00:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Follow me and\NI shall answer your hatred.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.20,0:00:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.54,0:00:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.96,0:00:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.34,0:01:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Open yourself!\NBecome one with my mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.80,0:01:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Demon Beast Invasion\Nepisode 4
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.66,0:01:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The snowfall which began\Nlast night lasted until noon...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.25,0:01:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and weather will be unsettled\Nfor the next few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.63,0:01:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Due to deep snowdrifts in the\NKansai region, travel is disrupted.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.34,0:01:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Asakura residence.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.30,0:01:50.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me.\NHow've you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.01,0:01:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miyuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.56,0:01:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know this is sudden, but wanna\Ncome up here for your school break?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.60,0:02:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? It is kinda sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.61,0:02:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.77,0:02:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been so lonely here since\NI came for shrine maiden training.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.65,0:02:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no friend here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.07,0:02:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really want to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.95,0:02:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I have plans...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.53,0:02:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're dating the son of\Nthe Ungyosai temple master?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.75,0:02:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? How did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.58,0:02:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm psychic, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.04,0:02:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So bring your boyfriend\Nwith you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.71,0:02:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.01,0:02:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll be coming\Nwhether you invite him or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.39,0:02:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.06,0:02:38.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said I was psychic.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.43,0:02:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two are possessed by\Nan evil hatred.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.73,0:02:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miyuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.73,0:02:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understand?\NYou have to be cleansed of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.36,0:02:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm your cousin,\Nso I can't ignore this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.07,0:02:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to be purified.\NSo I'm inviting you to Ohyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.74,0:02:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.45,0:02:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I promise I'll meet you\Nat the train station.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.66,0:03:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.96,0:03:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello? Hello?\NMiyuki? Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.44,0:03:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very good, Miyuki...\NLure them to Ohyarna...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.04,0:03:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? I didn't know\Nyou had a cousin like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.79,0:03:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.71,0:03:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's from a long\Nline of shrine maidens.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.59,0:03:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her predictions have\Nalways been dead on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.30,0:03:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't want to believe that\NDemon Beast is still after us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.14,0:03:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...\NThat worries me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.06,0:04:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maitreya'e returned\Nto normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.48,0:04:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to give a memorial\Nservice for the temple supporters.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.50,0:04:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the devil?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.84,0:04:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?\NIs the Ungyosai temple cursed?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.83,0:05:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muneto, I'm sorry!\NDid I bite you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.55,0:05:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all right, Kayo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.51,0:05:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muneto...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.59,0:05:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,MUNETO!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.89,0:05:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,MUNETO!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.52,0:05:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.56,0:05:28.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- We're cursed!\N- Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.73,0:05:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're cursed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.44,0:05:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something has corrupted\NMaitreya's power!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.11,0:05:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- I cannot exorcise it!\N- What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.15,0:05:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muneto, you share the\N1,100-year-old karmic debt...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.28,0:05:42.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...of the Ungyosai family\Nto the depths of your soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.24,0:05:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get a hold of yourself!.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.58,0:05:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with all this\Nanachronistic talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.83,0:05:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maitreya... Maitreya...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.88,0:05:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.09,0:05:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.25,0:05:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wander, lost in\Na world of torment!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.59,0:06:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother,\Nonly you can save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.14,0:06:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.60,0:06:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.94,0:06:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,KAYO!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.94,0:06:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naumaku Samanda\NAmidaunken Sowaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.61,0:06:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naumaku Samanda\NAmidaunken Sowaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.28,0:06:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naumaku Samanda\NAmidaunken Sowaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.84,0:06:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.18,0:06:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muneto!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.18,0:06:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muneto!\NGo to Ohyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.89,0:06:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maitreya will never forgive you\Nunless you end your evil karma!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.36,0:06:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To Ohyama...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.99,0:07:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Strange...\NIt's just like Miyuki said.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.16,0:07:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. So, we must purify\Nourselves of the Demon Beast.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.38,0:07:18.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can face anything\Nas long as I'm with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.17,0:07:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ohyama, where I will train at,\Nallows no women...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.34,0:07:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...into the forbidden sealed area.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.97,0:07:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Then what will I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.06,0:07:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Outside the sealed zone you'll\Nhave to have Miyuki purify you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.69,0:07:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have Miyuki...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.40,0:07:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A shrine maiden with\Ndivine powers in her blood...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.69,0:07:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...will be able to protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.24,0:07:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be safe until I return.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.78,0:07:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just feel...\NSorta nervous about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.10,0:08:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The evil moves to the west...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.98,0:09:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.94,0:09:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muneto...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.40,0:09:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Overshoot your station?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.37,0:09:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.04,0:10:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.22,0:10:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miyuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.38,0:10:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.01,0:10:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great, just great!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.39,0:10:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? You seem different.\NSexier.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.39,0:10:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.56,0:10:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, this is really weird.\NWe came together...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.56,0:10:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...just like you predicted.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.40,0:10:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Muneto Ungyosai.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.40,0:10:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.07,0:10:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, hello there.\NHmm, not bad at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.08,0:10:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Strange... Have we\Nmet somewhere before?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.66,0:10:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, time out! No pick-up lines\Nfor my boyfriend, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.05,0:10:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.59,0:10:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.68,0:10:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Strange... I DO feel like\NI know her from somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.43,0:10:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But where?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.22,0:10:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll take It easy tonight, then\Ngo to Ohyama tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.06,0:11:01.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like old times!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.10,0:11:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I thought\Nwomen aren't allowed into Ohyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.44,0:11:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll just go\Nup to the gates.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.78,0:11:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a waterfall there for\Nwomen to purify themselves in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.16,0:11:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.08,0:11:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muneto, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.75,0:12:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I beat my cursed destiny?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.51,0:12:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.52,0:12:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll wash your back, Muneto.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.62,0:12:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Miyuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.20,0:12:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Getting her photo album to show\Nyou. From when she was little
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.83,0:12:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's really going\Nout of her way for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.50,0:12:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.67,0:12:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.88,0:12:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be sleeping in\NMiyuki's room tonight, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.56,0:13:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.85,0:13:04.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.23,0:13:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Muneto.\NNot yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.62,0:14:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready, Kayo?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.12,0:14:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.14,0:14:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.51,0:15:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Oh, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.32,0:15:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo, I'm going to...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.89,0:15:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.90,0:15:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Uh, it tickles.\N- I love you, Kayo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.23,0:15:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you, Muneto.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.90,0:16:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow! You little...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.24,0:16:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Muneto, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.75,0:16:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Munechika... What do you\Nwant at this hour?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.59,0:16:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw ominous clouds\Nto the west.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.59,0:16:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've come to see if you were\Nall right, my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.77,0:16:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Being excommunicated from the\NUngyosai shrine leaders for my heresy...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.11,0:16:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had first thought\NI shouldn't interfere. However...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.90,0:16:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The temple votive statue is cursed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.61,0:16:46.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you know this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.62,0:16:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Ungyosai family,\Nloyal servants of the Buddha...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.62,0:16:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...once committed\Na grave sin against him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.00,0:16:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It has afflicted many of us\Nin the past, not just you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.96,0:16:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought\Nit would affect Muneto.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.26,0:17:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As things stand,\Nwe risk being cut off from...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.26,0:17:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...not only Maitreya's grace,\Nbut from all the gods!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.85,0:17:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And where's Muneto?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.64,0:17:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sent him to the main temple\Nto do his penance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.31,0:17:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!\NTo Ohyama?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.31,0:17:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you so\Nupset about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.02,0:17:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It could be a trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.27,0:17:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?\NThe temple is holy ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.32,0:17:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know the true nature\Nof the temple, my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.61,0:17:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.66,0:17:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ohyama is holy ground...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.83,0:17:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but there are evils\Nwhich await rebirth there...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.54,0:17:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and plot the overthrow\Nof the earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.83,0:17:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't mean...\NThe Demon Beast?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.34,0:17:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.34,0:17:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ohyama is insulated\Nfrom the demon realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.05,0:17:48.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ohyama is a world unto itself,\Ninsulated from the depths of man!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.10,0:17:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were naive!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.31,0:17:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.45,0:18:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sohnen, my love.\NIt's been so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.03,0:18:14.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A thousand years\NI've longed for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.70,0:18:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But at last I see you again.\NI'm so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.54,0:18:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sohnen...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.72,0:18:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Why do\Nyou flee from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.35,0:18:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.47,0:18:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No woman may enter\Nthe holy grounds of Ohyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.89,0:18:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now leave me in peace!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.44,0:18:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I will stay, though\Nit bring down the gods' wrath!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.40,0:18:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until you and I are man and wife!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.74,0:18:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.37,0:18:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A servant of the gods cannot\Nprofane his body with lust!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.41,0:19:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You take joy in\Nscarring my skin?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.04,0:19:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then please, end my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.42,0:19:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill me, and run.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.84,0:19:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill me, and I will only\Nkeep on following you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.43,0:19:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.44,0:19:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.94,0:19:25.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.78,0:19:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold me...\NHold me like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.17,0:19:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miyuki and I have met,\Nin our past lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.80,0:19:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.22,0:19:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.89,0:20:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.56,0:20:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo! Where are you?!\NKayo! Kayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.82,0:20:13.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miyuki, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.16,0:20:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is strange.\NMiyuki, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.71,0:20:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"NO WOMEN WITHIN THESE BOUNDS"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.50,0:20:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't we tell Muneto?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.53,0:20:51.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.20,0:20:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.87,0:20:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sohnen's scent...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.21,0:21:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are...? No!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.55,0:21:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.55,0:21:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A thousand years of\Nlonging shall be relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.18,0:21:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.18,0:21:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miyuki, what are you...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.56,0:21:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall offer you\Nto the Demon Beast.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.23,0:21:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Why?! Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.57,0:21:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo... You will pervert Ohyama's\Npower to the demon realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.91,0:21:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When this holy site which\Nforbids women is subverted...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.24,0:21:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the Demon Beast will be reborn!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.58,0:21:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.87,0:21:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miyuki, don't you know\Nhow horrible that would be?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.92,0:21:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the Demon Beast revives...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.13,0:21:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...my thousand years of\Nlonging will be answered!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.64,0:21:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.85,0:22:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.28,0:22:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miyuki, you've done it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.28,0:22:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The boundary between the mountain\Nand the shrine is breached!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.27,0:22:48.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.65,0:22:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muneto... Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.32,0:22:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am reborn!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.99,0:23:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo, your warmth\Nhas broken the barrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.24,0:23:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.00,0:23:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is time for my rebirth!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.00,0:23:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ecstasy! Paradise!\NI can't think anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.39,0:23:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!\NWhat is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.97,0:23:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is the karmic debt upon\NMuneto or brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.27,0:23:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The depth of the debt...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.02,0:23:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Demon Beast is using the\Nthousand year curse himself!.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.03,0:23:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't die, my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.07,0:23:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall cleanse the thousand\Nyear curse upon the Ungyosai!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.03,0:23:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mahm! Begone\Nstubborn and evil foe!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.54,0:23:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seven trials become\Nseven blessings!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.08,0:23:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naumaku Samanda Basaradan\NSenta Makarosha Dasabadaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.38,0:23:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Un Takara Gamman.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.71,0:23:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nahm! Begone,\Nstubborn and evil foe!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.46,0:23:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seven trials become\Nseven blessings!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.05,0:24:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Om A Miri Tatei\NZekara Un!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.73,0:24:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.09,0:24:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heaven! Heaven!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.09,0:24:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great Munetara, hurry!\NI can't wait anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.10,0:24:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.73,0:24:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.02,0:24:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How skilled you are,\NGreat Priest!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.77,0:24:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, small difference between\Nheaven and hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.15,0:25:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the ultimate ecstasy\Nto be found in this existence!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.11,0:25:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're one to talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.40,0:25:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your lust has floated in the\Nmountains for a thousand years.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.83,0:25:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a good ally to the\Ndemon beasts...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.37,0:25:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...priest who transcends\Nthis dimension!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.79,0:25:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ecstasy! Ecstasy!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.46,0:25:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More! More!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.13,0:25:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great Priest!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.42,0:25:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.14,0:25:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother...\NMother has still not come!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.60,0:25:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The power I need to break\Nfree of the demon realm...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.94,0:25:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother,\Nonly you can provide it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.50,0:25:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me. Have you seen\Ntwo girls around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.46,0:26:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Are you mad?\N- Ohyama is forbidden to women.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.71,0:26:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- But...\N- Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.84,0:26:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.47,0:26:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Space and time are\Nalready crumbling in Ohyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.39,0:26:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't those two see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.46,0:26:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uncle Munechika!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.55,0:26:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muneto, where's Kayo?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.55,0:26:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.89,0:26:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to get her out\Nof the sealed zone!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.22,0:26:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's the one subverting\NOhyama's holy power.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.18,0:26:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Kayo's with Miyuki,\Na girl I met in a former life.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.56,0:27:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought my brother\Nwas the only one.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.90,0:27:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the son also shares\Na lust-filled past life.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.90,0:27:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uncle! Tell me!\NWhat's happened to my father?!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.91,0:27:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He has assumed the form\Nof a past life...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.66,0:27:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and is helping the Demon Beast\Nto shatter the lust seal on Ohyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.42,0:27:21.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.25,0:27:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is karma.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.59,0:27:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You, his son, don't know\Nthe depths of his past sins.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.59,0:27:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even he doesn't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.93,0:27:30.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.93,0:27:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Without realizing he's become\Nthe Demon Beast's servant...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.93,0:27:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...he is soiling Ohyama...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.89,0:27:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...with the power of his lust\Nfor thousand-year-old spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.60,0:27:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.27,0:27:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this. You must\Nstill his breath with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.94,0:27:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I...\NI can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.61,0:27:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He will rape Kayo as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.24,0:27:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This hellish power is fed by\Nthe alien Demon Beast...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.58,0:27:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and the desires of\Na holy girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.87,0:28:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and will allow hirn to\Nbreach the seal on this place!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.96,0:28:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.88,0:28:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.97,0:28:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Liar! You want me\Nto give you more!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.97,0:28:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother, help rne! Why do\Nyou hide your true feelings?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.32,0:28:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.03,0:28:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The consciousness of the human\Nand Demon Beast realms...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.03,0:28:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...are mixing within your body!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.00,0:28:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Priest! They're open to you!\NBoth dripping holes!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.00,0:28:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, it's like a\Nwriggling worm.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.05,0:28:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Ungyosai! Stop it!\NNo, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.97,0:28:58.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muneto...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.02,0:29:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Ungyosai...!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.03,0:29:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take it!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.04,0:29:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.67,0:29:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which do you want?\NIt's your choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.71,0:29:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uncle...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.38,0:29:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your father or your lover?\NNow choose!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.69,0:29:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo! You belong to\Nthe Demon Beast!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.07,0:29:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Open your unwilling thighs!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.07,0:29:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miyuki... Stop this...\NThis can't be happening...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.41,0:30:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is!\NYou were born to steal Muneto's...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.41,0:30:04.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To steal Sohnen's heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.75,0:30:12.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.42,0:30:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muneto!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.38,0:30:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sohnen!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.76,0:30:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.76,0:30:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miyuki, stop this.\NI don't want to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.10,0:30:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sohnen, my love.\NI'll make you remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.10,0:30:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The warmth this part of\Nmy body felt for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.77,0:30:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!\NI'm not Sohnen!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.78,0:30:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's been dead a thousand years\Nand reborn as Muneto Ungyosai!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.78,0:30:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come, Sohnen!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.49,0:30:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miyuki, what's...?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.75,0:30:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've pursued you across a\Nmillennium. I won't lose you now!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.13,0:30:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So warm, is it not?\NCome into me!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.80,0:30:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold me. Embrace me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.14,0:31:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muneto!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.14,0:31:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! If you\Ndon't stop, I'll...!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.77,0:31:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lick me!\NTo my very depths...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.48,0:31:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.15,0:31:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miyuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.82,0:31:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.16,0:31:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muneto!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.20,0:31:24.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of the sealed zone!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.16,0:31:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you're in here and\NOhyama's holiness is subverted...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.12,0:31:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...we won't be able to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.83,0:31:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time of\Nconquest has come!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.46,0:31:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time of my vengeance\NI shall walk the earth again!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.20,0:32:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sohnen, my love!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.54,0:32:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's found us!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.88,0:32:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo, hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.22,0:32:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sohnen, wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.27,0:32:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muneto!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.24,0:32:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miyuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.78,0:32:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sohnen, my love.\NI'll never let you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.08,0:32:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muneto!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.25,0:32:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.75,0:32:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think of him as Muneto.\NHe has become Sohnen Ungyosai...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.46,0:33:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...holder of a\Nthousand years of karmic debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.76,0:33:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.80,0:33:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he doesn't settle the debt here,\Nyou two will never be one!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.93,0:33:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mister...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.27,0:33:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miyuki, turn back\Nto normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.77,0:33:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're being driven by\Nthe thousand years of lust...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.53,0:33:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the Demon Beast has unlocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.61,0:33:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sohnen, what are you saying?\NDo you reject me still?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.95,0:33:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have only one wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.25,0:33:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be with you, just once.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.92,0:33:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.\NI'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.30,0:33:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me... Yukino!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.34,0:33:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sohnen!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.63,0:33:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sohnen, my love!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.80,0:33:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukino!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.64,0:33:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sohnen!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.39,0:34:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.87,0:34:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sohnen!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.01,0:35:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sohnen!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.70,0:35:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sohnen!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.03,0:35:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sohnen, my love...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.29,0:35:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My regrets have left me...\NOh, joyous day!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.36,0:36:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn that thing!\NIt's broken the seal!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.78,0:36:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it all...!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.41,0:36:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.45,0:36:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miyuki, I've done it!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.79,0:36:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now kill the boy\Nbefore we descend the mountain!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.54,0:36:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then come to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.13,0:36:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.76,0:36:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miyuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.80,0:36:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! No! I won't!\NI can't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.81,0:36:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've found you, Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.52,0:36:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.14,0:36:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And your drips of\Nyour warm wetness!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.56,0:36:47.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By all means, come to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.11,0:36:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miyuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.49,0:36:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miyuki!\NWhat are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.49,0:36:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run!\NKayo, save yourself!.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.83,0:36:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Traitor!\NYou dare turn against me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.88,0:37:05.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miyuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.09,0:37:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muneto, your father!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.13,0:37:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.68,0:37:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father!\NYou've fallen into hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.81,0:37:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.87,0:37:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.12,0:37:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muneto, run for it!\NI'll handle this!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.50,0:37:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a marker at the summit\Nfor the mountain's guardian deity.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.88,0:37:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sealed zone ends there!\NYou can protect Kayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.55,0:37:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!\NBut, uncle...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.55,0:37:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.09,0:37:57.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Kayo, let's go!\N- Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.22,0:38:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother,\Nyou won't escape me!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.56,0:38:04.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.85,0:38:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impressive! You're more than\Nyou appear to be, monk!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.57,0:38:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Interplanetary Mutual\NObservation Agent: Panther!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.91,0:38:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You face ME now!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.25,0:38:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.59,0:38:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if my uncle's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.93,0:38:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what about Miyuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.60,0:38:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't escape me, Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.28,0:38:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,MOTHER!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.57,0:39:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Muneto!\N- Kayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.29,0:39:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go!\NUnhand me, traitor?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.29,0:39:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miyuki! No...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.46,0:39:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukino.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.80,0:39:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miyuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.84,0:39:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sohnen, my love...\NNo, Muneto I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.26,0:39:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for answering\Nmy desires.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.98,0:39:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have made me so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.61,0:39:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukino...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.65,0:39:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will let you go.\NHowever...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.32,0:39:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When we are reborn...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.32,0:39:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...we will be\Ntogether once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.99,0:39:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Farewell.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.00,0:39:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you\Nthink you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.02,0:40:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uncle!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.20,0:40:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I doing here...?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.55,0:40:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo... Kayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.72,0:40:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muneto!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.05,0:40:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo...\NI guess we made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.39,0:40:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.72,0:40:50.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As hot for each other as usual,\Nhuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.73,0:40:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miyuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.81,0:40:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miyuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.73,0:40:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miyuki, are you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.98,0:41:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not a bit!\NIn fact, I feel great!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.40,0:41:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness!
